anonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-shooting-nightclub-dead-injured-queens-amazura-new-year-day-125010200313_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRuined%20My%20Life%26quot%3B%3A%20Video%20Shows%20Expletive-Laden%20Chat%20Between%20Cafe%20Owner%2C%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20CCTV%20video%20has%20shown%20Delhi%20cafe%20owner%20Puneet%20Khurana%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20his%20estranged%20wife%20Manika%20Pahwa.%20The%20video%20of%20the%20expletive-laden%20exchange%20shows%20Pahwa%20accusing%20Khurana%20of%20ruining%20her%20life.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20go%20to%20your%20locality%20and%20create%20a%20scene.%20They%20keep%20crying%20on%20the%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20is%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-cafe-owner-dies-by-suicide-amid-divorce-business-dispute-with-wife-7375191%5C%22%3EKhurana%20(40)%20was%20found%20hanging%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20room%20in%20Model%20Town's%20Kalyan%20Vihar%20area%20on%20New%20Year's%20Eve.%20He%20had%20spoken%20to%20Pahwa%20on%20Monday%20night%20and%20recorded%20the%20conversation%2C%20in%20which%20the%20couple%20can%20be%20heard%20fighting%20over%20issues%20related%20to%20their%20co-owned%20bakery%20'For%20God's%20Cake'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2015-minute%20call%20recording%2C%20Pahwa%20was%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BBeggar%2C%20tell%20me%20what%20have%20you%20asked%20for.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20see%20your%20face.%20If%20you%20come%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20I%20will%20slap%20you.%20If%20the%20divorce%20is%20going%20on%2C%20will%20you%20remove%20me%20from%20the%20business%3F%20Then%20you%20will%20say%2C%20if%20you%20threaten%20me%2C%20I%20will%20commit%20suicide.%26quot%3B%20In%20response%2C%20the%20man%20dismissed%20her%20grievances%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20this%20doesn't%20matter%20anymore.%20Just%20tell%20me%20what%20you%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPahwa%20and%20Khurana%20got%20married%20in%202016%20and%20started%20the%20Woodbox%20Cafe%20together.%20After%20a%20year-and-a-half%20of%20being%20married%2C%20their%20relationship%20soured%20and%20by%20mutual%20consent%2C%20they%20moved%20court%20for%20a%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhurana's%20family%20alleged%20that%20Pahwa%20made%20five%20demands%20to%20settle%20their%20divorce%2C%20including%20Rs%2070%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20lawyer's%20fee.%20She%20also%20allegedly%20threatened%20to%20send%20the%20man%20and%20his%20family%20to%20jail%20if%20her%20demands%20were%20not%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man's%20family%20also%20said%20that%20their%20son%20made%20a%20video%20recording%20in%20his%20phone%20in%20which%20he%20has%20accused%20Pahwa%20of%20pressuring%20him%20over%20property%20and%20business%2C%20eventually%20pushing%20him%20to%20take%20the%20drastic%20step.%20Khurana's%20mother%20claimed%20Pahwa%20kept%20torturing%20her%20son%20and%20he%20suffered%20in%20silence.%20%26quot%3BThe%20two%20shared%20the%20business%2C%20they%20would%20have%20disputes%20over%20it.%20He%20would%20not%20say%20anything%20openly%20to%20us%2C%20thinking%20we%20would%20be%20upset.%20He%20kept%20swallowing%20his%20grief.%20My%20son%20was%20doing%20well%2C%20but%20she%20tortured%20him%20so%20much%20yesterday%20that%20he%20took%20this%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhurana's%20phone%2C%20which%20has%20the%20video%2C%20is%20with%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20as%20part%20of%20investigation%20into%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week%20before%20the%20suicide%2C%20Pahwa%20had%20put%20up%20a%20cryptic%20post%20on%20social%20media%20stating%20that%20she%20had%20been%20subjected%20to%20%26quot%3Btoxicity%20and%20narcissistic%20abuse%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20now%20free.%20Referring%20to%20her%20abusers%20as%20insecure%20cowards%2C%20Ms%20Pahwa%20said%20virtues%20like%20kindness%20and%20love%20are%20more%20important%20than%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhurana's%20death%20comes%20at%20the%20heels%20of%20techie%20Atul%20Subhash's%20suicide%20in%20Bengaluru%20last%20month.%20The%2034-year-old%20deputy%20general%20manager%20of%20a%20private%20firm%20left%20behind%20a%2024-page%20suicide%20note%2C%20accusing%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20relatives%20of%20harassment.%20According%20to%20the%20victim%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20had%20filed%20a%20slew%20of%20false%20cases%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20I%20work%20hard%20and%20become%20better%20at%20my%20work%2C%20the%20more%20l%20and%20my%20family%20will%20be%20harassed%20and%20extorted%20and%20the%20whole%20legal%20system%20will%20encourage%20and%20help%20my%20harassers...%20Now%2C%20with%20me%20gone%2C%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20money%20and%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20reason%20to%20harass%20my%20old%20parents%20and%20my%20brother.%20I%20may%20have%20destroyed%20my%20body%20but%20it%20has%20saved%20everything%20I%20believe%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Subhash's%20wife%20Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20and%20her%20mother%20and%20brother%20were%20arrested%20and%20sent%20to%2014-day%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735802040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F20v94qs8_cafe-owner-suicide_625x300_02_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fruined-my-life-video-shows-expletive-laden-chat-between-cafe-owner-wife-7382549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20CCTV%20video%20has%20shown%20Delhi%20cafe%20owner%20Puneet%20Khurana%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20his%20estranged%20wife%20Manika%20Pahwa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fruined-my-life-video-shows-expletive-laden-chat-between-cafe-owner-wife-7382549%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl