nsider.com%2F677596bc9de00e389eb41160%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223690%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20FBI%20has%20identified%20the%20driver%20in%20the%20attack%20on%20New%20Orleans%20as%2042-year-old%20US%20citizen%20Shamsud-Din%20Jabbar.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMatthew%20Hinton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFBI%20identified%20Shamsud-Din%20Jabbar%20as%20the%20suspect%20in%20the%20New%20Orleans%20truck%20attack.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJabbar%2C%20now%20deceased%2C%20was%20a%20US%20citizen%20from%20Texas%20and%20had%20a%20criminal%20record.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20least%2015%20people%20were%20confirmed%20dead%2C%20and%20dozens%20more%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Ffbi-statement-on-the-attack-in-new-orleans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentified%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20suspect%20in%20Wednesday's%20deadly%20attack%20in%20New%20Orleans%20as%20Shamsud-Din%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJabbar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20Jabbar%2C%20who%20was%20confirmed%20dead%20after%20a%20shootout%20with%20police%2C%20was%20a%2042-year-old%20US%20citizen%20from%20Texas.%20His%20actions%20are%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmass-casuality-event-reported-new-orleans-bourbon-and-canal-street-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20attack.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2015%20people%20are%20confirmed%20dead%2C%20and%20dozens%20more%20were%20injured%2C%20after%20the%20suspect%20drove%20a%20truck%20into%20crowds%20on%20Bourbon%20Street%20at%20about%203%3A15%20a.m.%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day.%20Two%20police%20officers%20were%20shot%20but%20are%20in%20stable%20condition.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20said%20an%20ISIS%20flag%2C%20as%20well%20as%20weapons%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20improvised%20explosive%20device%2C%20were%20found%20in%20the%20Ford%20F-150%20pick-up%20truck%20Jabbar%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20other%20IEDs%20were%20found%20in%20the%20French%20Quarter%2C%20and%20the%20agency%20is%20investigating%20Jabbar's%20potential%20connection%20to%20terrorist%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20that%2C%20hours%20before%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20suspect%20had%20posted%20videos%20%26quot%3Binspired%20by%20ISIS%2C%20expressing%20a%20desire%20to%20kill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJabbar's%20criminal%20record%2C%20obtained%20from%20the%20Texas%20Department%20of%20Public%20Safety%20and%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20shows%20two%20prior%20arrests%20in%202002%20and%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etheft%20of%20%2450-%24500.%20The%20other%20was%20for%20driving%20with%20an%20invalid%20license.%20Both%20were%20classified%20as%20misdemeanors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFBI%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAssistant%20Special%20Agent%20Alethea%20Duncan%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20FBI%20does%20not%20believe%20Jabbar%20acted%20alone.%20She%20did%20not%20specify%20how%20many%20additional%20suspects%20the%20agency%20is%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aggressively%20running%20down%20every%20lead%2C%20including%20those%20of%20his%20known%20associates%2C%26quot%3B%20Duncan%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20asking%20anyone%20who%20has%20information%2C%20video%2C%20or%20pictures%20to%20provide%20it%20to%20the%20FBI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20added%20that%20Jabbar%20was%20an%20Army%20veteran%2C%20and%20the%20FBI%20believes%20he%20was%20honorably%20discharged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20military%20spokespersons%20told%20media%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%20that%20Jabbar%20had%20served%20in%20the%20Army%20from%202007%20to%202015%2C%20during%20which%20he%20was%20deployed%20to%20Afghanistan%20from%20February%202009%20to%20January%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20filled%20information%20technology%20and%20human%20resource%20roles%20at%20the%20time%20and%20was%20later%20an%20information%20technology%20specialist%20in%20the%20Army%20Reserve%20from%202016%20until%202020.%20He%20left%20the%20military%20as%20a%20staff%20sergeant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJabbar%20also%20graduated%20from%20Georgia%20State%20University%20in%202017%20after%20studying%20information%20technology%2C%20per%20an%20online%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20reviewed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2025%2F01%2F01%2Fus%2Fshamsud-din-jabbar-suspect-new-orleans-attack%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Keenan%2C%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20for%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2025%2F01%2F01%2Fus%2Fnew-orleans-vehicle-crash%2Fthe-attacker-told-his-college-paper-that-he-struggled-to-adjust-to-life-after-the-military%3Fsmid%3Durl-share%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20that%20he%20had%20interviewed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Jabbar%20in%202015%20for%20Georgia%20State%20University's%20newspaper.%20Jabbar%20told%20Keenan%20that%20he%20had%20difficulty%20adjusting%20back%20to%20civilian%20life%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20with%20getting%20used%20to%20non-military%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20skills%20and%20training%20from%20the%20Army%2C%26quot%3B%20Jabbar%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20the%20article.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20speak%20the%20language%20to%20really%20translate%20it%20and%20be%20understood%20when%20you%20apply%20for%20a%20civilian%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJabbar%20had%20also%20complained%20that%20bureaucracy%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Veteran%20Affairs%20meant%20he%20might%20not%20receive%20his%20benefits%20if%20he%20made%20small%20mistakes%20on%20his%20paperwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Jabbar's%20resume%2C%20CNN%20reported%20that%20he%20worked%20at%20Deloitte%20and%20Accenture%2C%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20consultancies.%20A%20Deloitte%20spokesperson%20told%20CNN%20that%20he%20worked%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bstaff-level%20role%26quot%3B%20since%20his%202021%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccenture%20and%20Deloitte%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJabbar%20also%20held%20a%20real%20estate%20license%20in%20Texas%20from%202019%20to%202023.%20He%20took%20classes%20in%20real%20estate%20from%202018%20to%202021%2C%20per%20the%20Texas%20Real%20Estate%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECNN%20reported%20he%20had%20divorced%20twice%20and%20that%20his%20second%20ex-wife%20had%20a%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20against%20him%20granted%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuro%2C%20a%20carsharing%20company%2C%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20that%20Jabbar%20used%20a%20truck%20rented%20through%20its%20app%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20attack%20and%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bactively%20partnering%20with%20the%20FBI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20currently%20aware%20of%20anything%20in%20this%20guest's%20background%20that%20would%20have%20identified%20him%20as%20a%20trust%20and%20safety%20threat%20to%20us%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20reservation%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Turo%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20comes%20ahead%20of%20three%20major%20events%20in%20New%20Orleans%2C%20including%20the%20college%20football%20Sugar%20Bowl%20game%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20for%20January%201.%20Officials%20said%20it%20has%20been%20postponed%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20also%20has%20its%20annual%20Mardi%20Gras%20festivities%20starting%20on%20January%206%20and%20the%2059th%20Super%20Bowl%20scheduled%20for%20February%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuspect-deadly-new-orleans-attack-bourbon-street-new-years-eve-202