0Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20today%20expressed%20optimism%20regarding%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20to%20the%20region.%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20stripped%20of%20its%20special%20status%20and%20statehood%20and%20bifurcated%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20(UT)%20in%202019.%20Restoration%20of%20special%20status%20was%20a%20key%20promise%20in%20the%20National%20Conference%202024%20election%20manifesto.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20in%20power%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months%20now.%20It%20took%20us%20some%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20functioning%20of%20a%20government%20in%20a%20UT.%20It%20was%20easier%20than%20anticipated.%20We%20stand%20by%20the%20promises%20we%20made%20before%20the%20elections%20because%20of%20which%20people%20gave%20us%20the%20mandate%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20It%20will%20be%20of%20utmost%20importance%20to%20us%20to%20change%20the%20status%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20status%20of%20UT%20is%20a%20temporary%20phase%20for%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20participated%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20good%20numbers.%20The%20union%20government%20had%20promised%20statehood%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20it%20will%20not%20take%20much%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20statehood%20restoration%20over%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20elections%20were%20held%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202024%20after%20a%20decade.%20These%20were%20the%20first%20polls%20since%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370.%20They%20were%20also%20the%20first%20elections%20in%20which%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20cadres%2C%20banned%20in%202019%2C%20participated.%20The%20National%20Conference%20secured%2042%20out%20of%2090%20seats%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20remains%20the%20principal%20opposition%2C%20solidified%20its%20base%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%2C%20winning%2029%20of%20the%2043%20seats%20there.%20However%2C%20it%20continued%20to%20struggle%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20where%20it%20failed%20to%20secure%20a%20single%20seat.%20The%20Congress%20won%20six%20seats%20while%20the%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20saw%20a%20decline%2C%20managing%20only%20three%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%2C%20the%20new%20National%20Conference%20government%20passed%20a%20resolution%20calling%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20landmark%20resolution%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20demanding%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370.%20The%20BJP%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20move%2C%20leading%20to%20chaotic%20scenes%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20with%20over%20a%20dozen%20of%20its%20members%20being%20marshalled%20out%20during%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20formation%20of%20an%20elected%20government%2C%20governance%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20continues%20to%20operate%20under%20a%20hybrid%20model.%20Key%20administrative%20powers%2C%20including%20home%20affairs%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20transfer%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officers%2C%20remain%20with%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735800420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fr9hsv9v_omar-abdullah_625x300_16_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-jammu-and-kashmir-expect-j-k-statehood-to-be-restored-soon-omar-abdullah-7382339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22National%20Conference%20(NC)%20leader%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20today%20expressed%20optimism%20regarding%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20to%20the%20region.