%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ffight-to-the-end-impeached-south-korean-president-yoon-amid-detention-threat%2Famp_articleshow%2F116872248.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Court%20Denies%20Bail%20To%20Jailed%20Hindu%20Monk%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Bangladesh%20court%20on%20Thursday%20rejected%20the%20bail%20plea%20of%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%2C%20a%20Hindu%20monk%20and%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Sammilit%20Sanatan%20Jagran%20Jote%2C%20who%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20jailed%20by%20the%20local%20authorities%20on%20charges%20of%20sedition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChattogram%20Metropolitan%20Sessions%20Judge%20Md%20Saiful%20Islam%20refused%20to%20grant%20bail%20to%20Das%2C%20the%20former%20International%20Society%20for%20Krishna%20Consciousness%20(ISKCON)%20leader%2C%20following%20a%2030-minute%20hearing%2C%20held%20with%20heightened%20security%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%2011%20lawyers%20participated%20in%20his%20bail%20hearing%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bangladeshi%20publication%20The%20Daily%20Star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20bail%20petition%20stated%20that%20Das%20-%20a%20monk%20who%20is%20suffering%20from%20various%20diseases%20including%20diabetes%20and%20respiratory%20problems%20-%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20a%20false%20and%20fabricated%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20development%20%26quot%3Bsad%26quot%3B%2C%20Radha%20Raman%20Das%2C%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20ISCKON%20Kolkata%20urged%20the%20Bangladesh%20government%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Hindu%20monk%20gets%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20sad%20news.%20We%20know%20that%20the%20entire%20world%20was%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20this.%20Everyone%20was%20expecting%20Chinmoy%20Prabhu%20will%20get%20freedom%20in%20the%20new%20year%20-%20but%20even%20after%2042%20days%2C%20his%20bail%20was%20rejected%20in%20a%20hearing%20today...%20Bangladesh%20government%20should%20ensure%20that%20he%20gets%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20ISKCON%20priest%20was%20arrested%20from%20the%20Hazrat%20Shahjalal%20International%20Airport%20area%20of%20Dhaka%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20sedition%20case%2C%20among%20other%20charges%2C%20filed%20in%20Chattogram%20on%20November%2025.%20Earlier%2C%20his%20bail%20plea%20hearings%20had%20to%20be%20postponed%20as%20lawyers%20appearing%20for%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20were%20threatened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%20a%20Chattogram%20court%20denied%20him%20bail%20citing%20that%20the%20plea%20was%20rejected%20because%20Das%20did%20not%20have%20a%20lawyer's%20letter%20of%20attorney%20on%20his%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unrest%20in%20Bangladesh%20stems%20from%20the%20sedition%20charges%20filed%20against%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20for%20allegedly%20raising%20a%20saffron%20flag%20above%20Bangladesh's%20national%20flag%20in%20Chittagong%20on%20October%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20arrest%20had%20sparked%20protests%2C%20culminating%20in%20violent%20clashes%20between%20his%20followers%20and%20law%20enforcement%20outside%20the%20Chattogram%20Court%20Building%20on%20November%2027%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735799820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fninval3k_isckon-priest-hindu-priest-chinmoy-krishna-das_625x300_26_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-court-denies-bail-to-jailed-hindu-monk-chinmoy-krishna-das-7382182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Bangladesh%20court%20has%20again%20rejected%20the%20Hindu%20monk%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das'%20bail%20petition%20in%20a%20sedition%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-court-denies-bail-to-jailed-hindu-monk-chin