ce-and-greene-exploit-new-orleans-terror-attack-to-stir-anti-immigrant-sentiment-what-did-we-expect%2Farticleshow%2F116871074.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-vance-and-greene-exploit-new-orleans-terror-attack-to-stir-anti-immigrant-sentiment-what-did-we-expect%2Famp_articleshow%2F116871074.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-vance-and-greene-exploit-new-orleans-terror-attack-to-stir-anti-immigrant-sentiment-what-did-we-expect%2Famp_articleshow%2F116871074.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FBI%20Probes%20ISIS%20Angle%20In%20New%20Orleans%20Attack%2C%20Witnesses%20Describe%20'Insanity'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPolice%20Superintendent%20Anne%20Kirkpatrick%20said%20the%20man%2C%20%26quot%3Bhell-bent%20on%20carnage%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20run%20over%20as%20many%20people%20as%20he%20could%20in%20the%20city's%20famous%20French%20Quarter%2C%20an%20area%20that%20was%20packed%20with%20people%20celebrating%20the%20start%20of%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20FBI%20is%20investigating%20the%20incident%20as%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism.%20The%20attacker%20as%20Shamsud-Din%20Jabbar%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20%26quot%3BUS%20citizen%20from%20Texas%26quot%3B.%20Officials%20said%20he%20might%20not%20have%20been%20acting%20alone.%20%26quot%3BAn%20ISIS%20flag%20was%20located%20in%20the%20vehicle%2C%20and%20the%20FBI%20is%20working%20to%20determine%20the%20subject's%20potential%20associations%20and%20affiliations%20with%20terrorist%20organizations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FBI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20He%20served%20more%20than%2010%20years%20in%20the%20military%20as%20a%20human%20resource%20specialist%20and%20an%20IT%20specialist%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20which%20said%20Jabbar%20deployed%20to%20Afghanistan%20from%202009%20to%202010.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20YouTube%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20Jabbar%20--%20speaking%20with%20a%20southern%20US%20accent%20--%20boasted%20of%20his%20skills%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfierce%20negotiator%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20advertised%20his%20property%20management%20services%20to%20potential%20clients.%20Criminal%20records%20reported%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20show%20that%20Jabbar%20had%20two%20previous%20charges%20for%20minor%20offenses%20--%20one%20in%202002%20for%20theft%20and%20another%20in%202005%20for%20driving%20with%20an%20invalid%20license.%20Jabbar%20was%20twice-married%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20with%20his%20second%20marriage%20ending%20in%20divorce%20in%202022%2C%20when%20he%20detailed%20experiencing%20financial%20problems%20in%20an%20email%20to%20his%20wife's%20lawyer.%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20afford%20the%20house%20payment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reportedly%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20real%20estate%20company%20had%20lost%20more%20than%20%2428%2C000%20in%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20and%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20on%20thousands%20in%20credit%20card%20debt%20to%20pay%20for%20lawyers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20justification%20for%20violence%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20and%20we%20will%20not%20tolerate%20any%20attack%20on%20any%20of%20our%20nation's%20communities%2C.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20linked%20the%20attack%20to%20illegal%20immigration.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20said%20that%20the%20criminals%20coming%20in%20are%20far%20worse%20than%20the%20criminals%20we%20have%20in%20the%20country...%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20posted%20on%20social%20media.%20While%20the%20FBI%20has%20said%20that%20violent%20crime%20has%20sharply%20come%20down%20across%20the%20US%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20said%20the%20nation's%20crime%20rate%20%26quot%3Bis%20at%20a%20level%20that%20nobody%20has%20ever%20seen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWitnesses%20described%20terrifying%20scenes%20of%20%26quot%3Binsanity%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20likened%20to%20being%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bwar%20zone%26quot%3B.%20Zion%20Parsons%20told%20CNN%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20like%20a%20movie.%20That's%20the%20only%20way%20I%20can%20explain%20it.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20truck%20threw%20bodies%20in%20the%20air%20in%20its%20wake.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20bodies%20and%20blood%20and%20all%20the%20trash%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20describing%20scenes%20of%20victims%20crying%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20fetal%20position%20after%20the%20truck%20had%20passed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20incident%20came%20amid%20100%20per%20cent%20staffing%2C%20with%20an%20additional%20300%20officers%20assisting%20from%20partner%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%20It%20came%20on%20a%20day%20the%20French%20Quarter%20listed%20special%20deals%20for%20New%20Year's%2C%20including%20LGBTQ%20parties%20and%20a%20drag%20cabaret%20nearby%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%20It%20also%20came%20shortly%20before%20the%20city%20hosts%20a%20major%20football%20game%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Sugar%20Bowl%2C%20featuring%20teams%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Georgia%20and%20Notre%20Dame.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInternational%20condemnation%20poured%20with%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20his%20thoughts%20are%20with%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%20and%20the%20injured.%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20trust%20that%20those%20responsible%20for%20this%20terrible%20act%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20justice.%20Violence%2C%20terrorism%2C%20and%20any%20threats%20to%20human%20life%20have%20no%20place%20in%20our%20world%20and%20must%20not%20be%20tolerated.%20Our%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims...%20Ukraine%20stands%20with%20the%20American%20people%20and%20denounces%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20separate%20incident%2C%20at%20least%20one%20person%20was%20killed%20and%20seven%20wounded%20when%20a%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20exploded%20outside%20a%20hotel%20belonging%20to%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20police%20said%20Wednesday.%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20authorities%20were%20investigating%20any%20links%20between%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20explosion%20and%20the%20New%20Orleans%20attack.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20FBI%20and%20local%20law%20enforcement%20said%20they%20believed%20the%20Tesla%20blast%20was%20an%20isolated%20incident.%20However%2C%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20chief%20Elon%20Musk%20alleged%20a%20connection%20between%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20and%20New%20Orleans%20attacks.%20%26quot%3BAppears%20likely%20to%20be%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism.%20Both%20this%20Cybertruck%20and%20the%20F-150%20suicide%20bomb%20in%20New%20Orleans%20were%20rented%20from%20Turo.%20Perhaps%20they%20are%20linked%20in%20some%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735791780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9kfr8jng_new-orleans-attack_625x300_02_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-orleans-attack-fbi-investigates-isis-angle-witnesses-describe-insanity-7381594%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20Army%20veteran%20ploughed%20a%20pick-up%20truck%20into%20a%20crowd%20of%20New%20Year%20revellers%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20killing%20at%20least%2015%20people%20and%20injuring%20dozens.%20The%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20said%20the%20accused%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20exchange%20of%20gunfire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-orleans-attack-fbi-investigates-isis-angle-witnesses-describe-insanity-7381594%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sacked%20Israeli%20defence%20mi