20after%20graduating%20from%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Favour%20the%20common%20man%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20Rs%205.65%20lakh%20crore%20has%20been%20written%20off%20for%20the%20industrial%20sector.%20Agriculture%2C%20the%20largest%20employer%20in%20the%20country%2C%20received%20the%20least%20attention%20in%20terms%20of%20loan%20write-offs%20among%20all%20sectors%20from%20Scheduled%20Commercial%20Banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Provide%20food%20for%20all%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Annually%2C%2017%20lakh%20Indians%20die%20from%20diseases%20related%20to%20insufficient%20food%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Ensure%20equal%20wages%20for%20all%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnnual%20growth%20rate%20of%20real%20wages%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20has%20been%20close%20to%20zero%20at%20the%20all-India%20level.%20Rural%20real%20wages%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%20have%20declined%20at%200.4%25%20and%20agricultural%20wages%20have%20become%20stagnant%20at%200.2%25.%20Four%20out%20of%20five%20people%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%20515%20as%20of%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Ensure%20dignity%20of%20life%20for%20farmers%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20per%20the%20NCRB%2C%2030%20farmers%20commit%20suicide%20every%20day.%20Since%20February%202024%2C%2022%20farmers%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20over%20160%20have%20been%20injured%20while%20protesting%20for%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Enable%20safety%20for%20women%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESection%2063%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20deals%20with%20the%20offence%20of%20rape%20but%20provides%20an%20exception%20for%20marital%20rape%2C%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9Csexual%20intercourse%20or%20sexual%20acts%20by%20a%20man%20with%20his%20own%20wife%2C%20the%20wife%20not%20being%20under%20eighteen%20years%20of%20age%2C%20is%20not%20rape%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E11.%20Ensure%20dignity%20for%20the%20marginalised%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBetween%202018%20and%202020%2C%20443%20people%20died%20cleaning%20sewers%20and%20septic%20tanks.%20Manual%20scavenging%20was%20banned%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E12.%20Protect%20the%20press%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Between%202014%20and%202019%2C%20there%20were%20200%20serious%20attacks%20on%20journalists%2C%20along%20with%20arrests%20and%20interrogations.%20At%20least%20194%20journalists%20were%20targeted%20by%20government%20agencies%2C%20non-state%20political%20actors%2C%20criminals%2C%20and%20armed%20opposition%20groups%20in%202022%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E13.%20Ensure%20equitable%20representation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20merely%2013.6%25.%20This%20is%20even%20less%20than%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20had%2014.4%25%20women.%20Only%20two%20out%20of%2024%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committees%20are%20chaired%20by%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E14.%20Allow%20legislative%20scrutiny%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%202019%2C%20over%20100%20bills%20have%20been%20passed%20in%20less%20than%20two%20hours.%20In%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20nine%20out%20of%2010%20bills%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20have%20been%20marked%20by%20zero%20or%20incomplete%20consultations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E15.%20Select%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20did%20not%20have%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20for%20its%20entire%20five-year%20term.%20The%20office%20of%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20continues%20to%20remain%20vacant%20even%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E16.%20Allow%20criticism%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20number%20of%20opposition%20MPs%20who%20have%20been%20suspended%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20has%20increased%2013-fold.%20As%20many%20as%2095%25%20cases%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20those%20from%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E17.%20Respect%20institutions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20National%20Commission%20for%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20do%20not%20have%20a%20Vice-Chairperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E18.%20Support%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20%26amp%3B%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20of%20March%202024%2C%20one%20out%20of%2010%20Kasturba%20Gandhi%20Balika%20Vidyalayas%20(KGBV)%20were%20not%20functional.%20Two%20out%20of%20five%20Eklavya%20schools%20were%20not%20functional%20as%20of%20July%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E19.%20Complete%20timelines%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%202021%20Census%20has%20still%20not%20been%20conducted.%20This%20makes%20it%20the%20first%20Census%20to%20be%20delayed%20between%201887%20and%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E20.%20Utilise%20funds%20better%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20much%20as%2080%25%20of%20the%20Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao's%20total%20fund%20was%20spent%20on%20media%20advocacy%2C%20not%20for%20interventions%20on%20health%20or%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E21.%20Release%20dues%20owed%20to%20states%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20government%20owes%20Rs%201%2C500%20Crore%20under%20MGNREGS%20and%20Awas%20Yojana%20to%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20non-payment%20of%20the%20funds%20has%20directly%20affected%20the%20livelihood%20of%2059%20lakh%20MGNREGS%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E22.%20Care%20about%20Manipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20continued%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20causing%20the%20displacement%20of%2067%2C000%20people%2C%20of%20which%2014%2C000%20are%20school-going%20students.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20yet%20to%20visit%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E23.%20Safeguard%20minorities%20and%20their%20welfare%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20NCRB%20recorded%20378%20instances%20of%20communal%20violence%20in%202021%20and%20272%20such%20instances%20in%202022.%20In%202023%2C%20India%20witnessed%20668%20documented%20hate%20speech%20incidents%20against%20one%20community%20alone.%20One%20hundred%20and%20twenty-eight%20properties%20were%20demolished%20between%20April%20and%20June%202022%2C%20following%20communal%20violence%20and%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E24.%20Build%20secure%20public%20infrastructure%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20were%20244%20train%20accidents%20between%202017%20and%202022.%20As%20many%20as%20135%20people%20died%20when%20a%20suspension%20bridge%20collapsed%20in%20Morbi.%20Fourty-one%20workers%20were%20trapped%20for%2017%20days%20after%20the%20Uttarkashi%20Tunnel%20caved%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E25.%20Enable%20a%20safer%20internet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Frauds%20relating%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdigital%20arrests%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20first%20nine%20months%20of%202024%20amounted%20to%20losses%20worth%20Rs%201616%20crore.%20The%20Digital%20Data%20Protection%20Rules%20have%20not%20been%20notified%20despite%20the%20Act%20being%20passed%20over%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Research%20credit%3A%20Varnika%20Mishra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735788180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmcg2vvcg_pm-modi_625x300_22_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-modi-governments-25-things-to-do-in-2025-7381343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Youth%20unemployment%20rate%20has%20been%20at%2010%25%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20As%20per%20the%20Economic%20Survey%2C%20half%20of%20all%20individuals%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20be%20employed%2