t.%20A%20constant%20drizzle%20is%20also%20likely%20on%20day%20five%20of%20the%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20as%20per%20BBC%20Weather%2C%20there%20could%20be%20some%20rain%20on%20Friday%20afternoon.%20During%20the%20weekend%2C%20there%20will%20be%20some%20sunshine.%20There%20is%20a%2068%20per%20cent%20chance%20of%20rain%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Monday%2C%20the%20day%20four%20of%20the%20match%2C%20but%20the%20weather%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20clear%20during%20the%20day's%20play.%20Day%20five%2C%20however%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20heavy%20showers%2C%20which%20will%20continue%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20affected%20by%20form%20of%20their%20key%20batters%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20who%20have%20scored%20just%20one%20fifty-plus%20score%20throughout%20the%20series%20combined.%20Despite%20some%20incredible%20bowling%20from%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20who%20has%20taken%2030%20wickets%20in%20four%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2012.83%2C%20India%20have%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20big%20impact%20in%20the%20series%20and%20are%20trailing%20by%201-2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20facing%20injury%20concerns%20with%20pacer%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20series%20due%20to%20calf%20injuries.%20Also%2C%20recent%20reports%20suggest%20that%20another%20frontline%20pacer%20Mitchell%20Starc%20has%20been%20sent%20for%20scans%20two%20days%20before%20the%20Sydney%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20is%202-1%20in%20favour%20of%20Australia%20and%20they%20are%20in%20a%20strong%20position%20to%20join%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship.%20However%2C%20if%20India%20wins%20the%20match%20and%20draws%20the%20series%2C%20not%20only%20they%20will%20retain%20the%20trophy%20again%2C%20but%20will%20also%20keep%20themselves%20alive%20in%20the%20WTC%20race%2C%20given%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Australia-Sri%20Lanka%20series%20next%20yea