20that%20used%20to%20be%20our%20trade.%20They%20also%20used%20to%20sell%20cattle%20to%20farmers%20who%20needed%20them%20for%20agriculture.%20At%20cattle%20fairs%20organised%20by%20the%20Government%2C%20they%20would%20buy%20and%20take%20the%20cattle%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20mainly%20to%20the%20southern%20regions.%20There%2C%20tribal%20farmers%20rely%20on%20cattle%20for%20farming%20instead%20of%20using%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20transportation%20methods%20improved%20and%20small%20markets%20began%20setting%20up%2C%20this%20line%20of%20business%20became%20obsolete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20then%20had%20to%20look%20for%20other%20ways%20of%20earning.%20With%20few%20options%20available%2C%20they%20shifted%20to%20labour%20work%20and%20formed%20a%20small%20community%20of%20labourers%20where%20everyone%20would%20work%20together.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20they%20decided%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20settle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paras%20Banjara%20addressing%20a%20Jan%20Sunwai%20to%20empower%20nomadic%20communities%20and%20help%20them%20raise%20their%20voices%20on%20important%20issues.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734