de%20of%20his%20community%2C%20Paras%20had%20to%20constantly%20fight%20a%20feeling%20of%20loneliness%20and%20isolation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20go%20to%20school%2C%20but%20because%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20to%20anyone%20as%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20language%2C%20and%20because%20the%20children%20also%20refused%20to%20speak%20to%20me%20because%20of%20my%20background%2C%20it%20was%20overwhelming.%20I%20ended%20up%20skipping%20school%20for%20many%20days%20out%20of%20fear%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20poverty%20to%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Paras%20graduated%20high%20school%2C%20his%20early%20experiences%20had%20shaped%20his%20understanding%20of%20social%20inequality%20and%20injustice.%20Whether%20it%20was%20watching%20his%20parents%20struggle%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20financial%20resources%2C%20being%20unable%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20authorities%20about%20their%20issues%2C%20or%20being%20at%20the%20epicenter%20of%20the%20problems%20his%20community%20faced%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20education%20became%20a%20crucial%20tool%20for%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20lack%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20poverty.%20My%20parents%20spent%20whatever%20they%20could%20to%20help%20me%20finish%20my%20education.%20When%20you%20grow%20up%20like%20this%2C%20by%20the%20time%20you%20finish%20studying%2C%20your%20one%20and%20only%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20a%20job%20that%20gives%20you%20security%20and%20a%20place%20in%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20admits.%20But%20right%20after%20school%2C%20he%20found%20out%20about%20%3Cem%3EMazdoor%20Kisan%20Shakti%20Sangathan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(MKSS)%2C%20a%20prominent%20organisation%20that%20demands%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20fair%20wages%20for%20workers%2C%20and%20while%20the%20need%20for%20a%20well-%20positioned%20job%20was%20ever%20present%2C%20Paras%20decided%20to%20commit%20to%20what%20he%20believed%20in%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20hardships%20that%20might%20follow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20organisation%2C%20he%20earned%20a%20meagre%20Rs%202%2C190%20per%20month%2C%20the%20same%20as%20everyone%20else.%20Given%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20time%2C%20his%20family%20was%20skeptical%20about%20how%20this%20would%20work%20out%20practically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20quite%20difficult%20to%20convince%20my%20family%2C%20especially%20after%20spending%20so%20much%20money%20on%20my%20education%2C%20that%20I%20was%20settling%20for%20just%20that%20much%20a%20month.%20But%20I%20was%20adamant.%20I%20had%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20work%20for%20myself%2C%20I%20had%20to%20do%20more%20than%20that.%20And%20I%20never%20regretted%20that%20decision%20because%20that%20organisation%20was%20God-sent%20for%20me.%20There%2C%20I%20learnt%20what%20equality%20meant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEstablishing%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20of%20identity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20pressing%20concerns%20for%20our%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20shares%2C%20noting%20that%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318643%2Fengineer-helps-mir-nomadic-community-gujarat-sell-traditional-beadwork-tokar-designs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enomadic%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E%20lack%20basic%20identity%20documents%20like%20ration%20cards%2C%20voter%20IDs%2C%20and%20birth%20certificates.%20Without%20these%20documents%2C%20they%20are%20excluded%20from%20government%20schemes%2C%20unable%20to%20access%20education%2C%20and%20often%20denied%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20very%20visible%20in%20mainstream%20social%20discourse.%20And%20because%20of%20the%20physical%20distance%20between%20the%20tribes%20and%20settled%20communities%2C%20there%20is%20a%20social%20and%20cultural%20distance%2C%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Added%20to%20the%20social%20stigma%20is%20political%20ignorance.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20our%20relatively%20small%20and%20scattered%20populations%2C%20political%20parties%20also%20overlook%20nomadic%20communities%20in%20their%20campaigns%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20with%20MKSS%20for%20years%20and%20studying%20social%20work%2C%20Paras%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20pressing%20issues%20and%20mobilise%20people%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20He%20focused%20on%20creating%20small%2C%20tight-knit%20communities%20within%20larger%20communities%2C%20where%20those%20who%20could%2C%20would%20support%20others%20and%20work%20together%20to%20address%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20common%20concerns%20that%20emerged%20was%20how%20to%20secure%20these%20documents%20for%20nomadic%20people.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20struggled%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20beginning%20with%20how%20to%20make%20these%20issues%20visible%2C%20understandable%2C%20and%20addressable%20to%20all%20stakeholders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20shares.%20Something%20as%20simple%20as%20getting%20a%20caste%20certificate%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20difficult%20and%20confusing%20process%20for%20many%2C%20including%20the%20lower-level%20government%20officials%20in%20offices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20some%20places%2C%20the%20lower%20bureaucracy%20was%20a%20bit%20more%20proactive%20and%20willing%20to%20help%2C%20others%20found%20themselves%20stuck%20in%20the%20process%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20the%20social%20structure%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262912%2Fdalit-woman-inspires-girl-child-education-uttar-pradesh-skvs-founder%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaste%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewithin%20the%20nomadic%20communities%2C%20Paras%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CHelping%20people%20navigate%20these%20bureaucratic%20hurdles%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20obtaining%20a%20caste%20certificate%2C%20meeting%20with%20the%20tehsildar%20or%20collector%2C%20or%20working%20with%20the%20principal%20secretary%20%E2%80%94%20helped%20clear%20the%20obstacles%20that%20hold%20them%20back%20from%20accessing%20crucial%20opportunities%20and%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.26.28-AM-1734609121.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olakhaan%20Trust%20supports%20nomadic%20groups%20by%20guiding%20them%20through%20the%20documentation%20process%20with%20the%20help%20of%20dedicated%20volunteers%20and%20workers.%5C%