earning%20and%20support%20has%20led%20to%20lasting%20relationships%20among%20its%20students.%20%E2%80%9CKids%20were%20coming%20in%20at%2011th%20grade%2C%20and%20we%20would%20help%20them%20until%20they%20got%20a%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20explains.%20Many%20students%2C%20who%20had%20been%20coming%20to%20Niwant%20for%20years%2C%20ended%20up%20marrying%20one%20another.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20an%20only%20child%2C%20and%20I%20always%20wanted%20siblings.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20had%20a%20big%20family%20of%20visually%20impaired%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329201%2Fgrailmaker-innovations-vision-nanny-platform-app-solution-for-kids-cortical-visual-impairment%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETech%20Vision%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20software%20company%20that%20started%20as%20part%20of%20Niwant%2C%20is%20another%20example%20of%20the%20impact%20Niwant%20has%20had.%20%E2%80%9CSiddhant%20Chothe%2C%20one%20of%20our%20students%20who%20lost%20his%20vision%20later%20in%20life%2C%20was%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20job%20despite%20having%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20computer%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20many%20unsuccessful%20attempts%20at%20getting%20Siddhant%20a%20job%2C%20the%20Niwant%20family%2C%20realising%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20anyone%20else%2C%20decided%20to%20start%20something%20of%20their%20own.%20With%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20Siddharth%20launched%20Tech%20Vision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-124_11zon-1734330345.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Visually%20impaired%20individuals%20from%20Niwant%20playing%20chess%2C%20promoting%20strategic%20